CatDescriptText: Ayona Richardson wearing solid suit 2nd from left, Jemitta Moore Andres 2nd from right, Mrs. Edmonds 2nd from right in front- owned flower shop, unknown lady on left end from browns chapter of Harriet Tubman Guild.  Georgia Quash possibly at podium.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve women, including Iona Richardson, Jemitta Moore Andres, Mrs. Edmonds, and Georgia Quash, Margaret Bartlett wearing eyeglasses and pearls, and man standing around podium with banner inscribed "Harriet Tubman Guild, Inc. 1915-1953" in church interior
